{
  "name": "aisdlc",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "> **Audience**: Developers, Tech Leads, Architects   > **Total Duration**: ~55 min mandatory + ~30 min optional (see two-track map below)   > **Pre-requisites**: VS Code with GitHub Copilot Chat extension, Node/Python/Java runtime, Git CLI, GitHub Copilot access, GitHub MCP, Mermaid extension for VS code.",
